            'editor' => '<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:18.0pt"><span style="color:black">TRAYECTORIA DE COLORES</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:18.0pt"><span style="color:#4040ab">PREGUNTAR E IMAGINAR</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#201c20">&iquest;Qu&eacute; es una trayectoria? &iquest;Qu&eacute; es el desplazamiento?</span></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#201c20">Para conocer m&aacute;s acerca de estos conceptos vamos a observar el siguiente video.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#201c20">Cinem&aacute;tica 3D: Trayectoria, Distancia y Desplazamiento:</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#201c20">Duraci&oacute;n: 4:27 minutos</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#e93440"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kXa3BRRdlH" style="color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kXa3BRRdlH</a></span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#201c20">Despu&eacute;s de observar el video contesta:</span></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#201c20">&iquest;Qu&eacute; es la trayectoria?</span></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#201c20">&iquest;Qu&eacute; es desplazamiento?</span></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="color:#201c20">&iquest;Cu&aacute;l es la f&oacute;rmula para obtener el desplazamiento?</span></span></span></span></p>

