<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Observa con cuidado las siguientes im&aacute;genes.</strong></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/6/RATONERA1.jpg" style="float:left; height:153px; width:230px" />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>

