<td style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Algoritmo</span></span></td>
<td style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Bloque de programaci&oacute;n</span></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</td>
<td>
<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<hr />
<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#ffffff"><strong><span style="background-color:#e67e22">&nbsp; ANALIZAR&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Describe c&oacute;mo se comunican la Antena satelital y el Sat&eacute;lite que ensamblaron.&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Por qu&eacute; crees que se deban comunicar de esta manera?</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Qu&eacute; otros aparatos conoces que se comuniquen inal&aacute;mbricamente?&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<hr />
<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/259/foco.jpg" style="float:left; height:173px; width:230px" />Modifiquen la programaci&oacute;n de sus ensambles para mandar diferentes mensajes al Sat&eacute;lite.&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<hr />
<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Una vez que terminen con las atividades, contesta el siguiente cuestionario:</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><iframe align="middle" frameborder="0" height="800" longdesc="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdh1QsarPF8bQwvng3A0O0MO6KhR_VdQPP8a_LYN0ZC8BP27Q/viewform?usp=sf_link" name="Cuestionario de Clase" scrolling="yes" src="https://forms.gle/agSQnUih54pqXwXHA" title="CUESTIONARIO" width="1000"></iframe></p>',
'level_id' => NULL,
'created_at' => '2019-07-30 15:33:20',
'updated_at' => '2019-08-30 17:51:19',
