Tiempo: &nbsp;1:30 min &nbsp; &nbsp;En los Estados Unidos, las ciudades de San Francisco y Pittsburgh contar&aacute;n para el a&ntilde;o 2020 con carros aut&oacute;nomos.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="color:#2ecc71"><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">DISE&Ntilde;AR Y CONTRUIR</span></span></span></strong></p>

<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Dise&ntilde;aremos un modelo base, al que daremos instrucciones b&aacute;sicas para calcular que distancia recorre por cada rotaci&oacute;n, y haremos algunos c&aacute;lculos matem&aacute;ticos que nos ayuden a establecer el inicio de un veh&iacute;culo aut&oacute;nomo.</span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos/loGO-ex.PNG" style="height:114px; width:686px" /></span></p>

<p><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px"><a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/18/ROBOT BASE PARTE1.pdf" onclick="window.open(this.href, \'\', \'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=yes,scrollbars=no,dependent=no\'); return false;"><input name="MODELO BASE (RC)" type="button" value="CONSTRUCTOR" /></a></span><span style="font-size:14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/18/ROBOT BASE PARTE2.pdf" onclick="window.open(this.href, \'\', \'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=yes,scrollbars=no,dependent=no\'); return false;"><input name="ROBOT BASE (RC)" type="button" value="COLABORADOR" /></a></span><span style="font-size:14px">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/18/Mi auto del futuro.pdf" onclick="window.open(this.href, \'\', \'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no\'); return false;"><input name="PROGRAMACION" type="button" value="PROGRAMA" /></a></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/18/Robot y distancia.JPG" style="height:140px; width:721px" /></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Junto con tu equipo realiza las siguientes programaciones y encuentra los resultados.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos/LOGO14.PNG" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">1. Tienes que lograr que tu veh&iacute;culo avance exactamente 50 cm.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">2. Debes lograr que tu robot retroceda de 100 cm a 75 cm.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">3. Debes lograr que tu robot avance exactamente 100 cm y despu&eacute;s retroceda hasta llegar a 80 cm.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><iframe align="middle" frameborder="0" height="800" longdesc="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfq35f5Lz8_vGNI5typtt8z68j4LnZ464XaibEJ2Tb3W15dGg/viewform?usp=sf_link" name="Cuestionario de Clase" scrolling="yes" src="https://forms.gle/YUn59hiaD7ShzMz18" title="CUESTIONARIO" width="1000"></iframe></span></span></p>',
