<p><span style="font-size:16px">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:26px"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos/LOGO6.PNG" style="height:32px; width:223px" /></span></span></p>

