<p><span style="font-size:16px"><a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/6/ROBOT BASE PARTE1.pdf" onclick="window.open(this.href, \'\', \'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no\'); return false;"><input name="Boton" type="button" value="Constructor" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/6/ROBOT BASE PARTE2.pdf" onclick="window.open(this.href, \'\', \'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no\'); return false;"><input name="Botón" type="button" value="Colaborador" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/18/Guia programación 4o (Introductoria brick).pdf" onclick="window.open(this.href, \'\', \'resizable=no,status=no,location=no,toolbar=no,menubar=no,fullscreen=no,scrollbars=no,dependent=no\'); return false;"><input name="Boton1" type="button" value="Programador" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">*Recuerda que el primer reto es lograr que tu robot avance por 2 segundos al frente, el segundo reto&nbsp;es que retroceda por 3 segundos.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:16px"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/18/Analizar.JPG" style="height:144px; width:124px" /></span><span style="font-size:20px">Analiza qu&eacute; hiciste para que tu robot realice las &oacute;rdenes que le diste.</span></p>

