'name' => 'Magnitudes y Proporcionalidad',
'description' => NULL,
'picture' => 'http://therobotcenterapp.com/PortadasCursos/CursoDefault.png',
'editor' => '<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos/LOGO.PNG" style="height:62px; width:123px" /></p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos/logo36.PNG" />&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="background-color:#f1c40f">&nbsp; PREGUNTAR E IMAGINAR&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>&iquest;Qu&eacute; son las magnitudes y qu&eacute; relacion tienen con la proporcionalidad?</strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Observa con atenci&oacute;n el siguiente video y responde las preguntas. (Para el tema de nuestra clase, no es necesario ver todo el video solo entre el minuto 0:00 y 5:40)(Usaremos una regla como material extra)</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos/logo37.PNG" /></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos/LOGO3.PNG" />Las aventuras de Troncho y Poncho: Proporcionalidad.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Duraci&oacute;n: 09:04&nbsp;<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9QjVXWqS8Q4">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9QjVXWqS8Q4</a></strong></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>&iquest;Qu&eacute; es una magnitud?</strong></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>&iquest;Qu&eacute; es la proporcionalidad?</strong></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Escribe dos ejempls de magnitud.</strong></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos/LOGO6.PNG" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos/logo38.PNG" /></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:26px"><strong><span style="background-color:#2ecc71">&nbsp; DISE&Ntilde;AR Y CONSTRUIR&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Para conocer m&aacute;s sobre las magnitudes y la proporcionalidad, utilizaremos nuestros robots durante la clase.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos/logo39.PNG" /></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="background-color:#c0392b">&nbsp;CONSTRUCTOR:&nbsp;</span></span></strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/253/VIAJERO PARTE1.pdf" target="_blank"><input name="Boton" type="button" value="CONSTRUCTOR" /></a>&nbsp; </span></span></p>

<p><strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="background-color:#2980b9">&nbsp;COLABORADOR:&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></strong>&nbsp;<span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/253/VIAJERO PARTE2.pdf" target="_blank"><input name="Boton1" type="button" value="COLABORADOR" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="background-color:#f39c12">&nbsp;PROGRAMADOR:&nbsp;</span></span></strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/253/GUIA PROGRAMACION 4o (1) 12.pdf" target="_blank"><input name="Boton" type="button" value="PROGRAMADOR" /></a></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>ACTIVIDADES PARA EL PROGRAMADOR:</strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Para realizar la programaci&oacute;n del ensamble &quot;Viajero&quot;, debes considerar las siguientes acciones.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">1) Deber&aacute;s entrar a Brick Program.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">2) Coloca un icono de mover direcci&oacute;n al inicio de tu programa.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">3) Coloca un icono de tiempo y presionar el bot&oacute;n del centro para escoger 2 segundos.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">4) Por &uacute;ltimo coloca un icono de mover direcci&oacute;n y presiona el bot&oacute;n del centro para escoger la opci&oacute;n detener.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">En base a las instrucciones anteriores, dibuja c&oacute;mo debe ser la programaci&oacute;n.</span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Ayud&aacute;ndote de una regla, mide la distancia que recorre tu robot en dos segundos. Completa los espacios vacios con la informaci&oacute;n correcta.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">2 segundos =&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; cent&iacute;metros.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos/LOGO14.PNG" /></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Las magnitudes de tiempo (segundos) y distancias (cent&iacute;metros) est&aacute;n relacionadas entre s&iacute;. Calcula cu&aacute;nto recorrer&aacute; el robot en los siguientes tiempos.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Tu Robot avanza 4 segundos: &iquest;Qu&eacute; distancia avanzar&aacute;?</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;cm.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Tu Robot avanza 5 segundos: &iquest;Qu&eacute; distancia avanzar&aacute;?</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;cm.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Tu Robot avanza 8 segundos: &iquest;Qu&eacute; distancia avanzar&aacute;?</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;cm.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Podemos decir que las anteriores Magnitudes son directamente proporcionales entre ellas? Si:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;No.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Por qu&eacute;?</span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos/LOGo23.PNG" />Dibuja tus prgramaci&oacute;nes de la secci&oacute;n Innovar.</span></span></p>

