124 => 
array (
'id' => 137,
'code' => '3.1.6',
'name' => 'MENTE SANA Y CUERPO SANO',
'description' => NULL,
'picture' => 'http://therobotcenterapp.com/PortadasCursos/CursoDefault.png',
'editor' => '<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos2/Eduktroic.PNG" style="height:57px; width:135px" /></p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos2/Logo34.PNG" style="height:22px; width:688px" /></p>

<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="background-color:#f1c40f">&nbsp; PREGUNTAR E IMAGINAR&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></strong></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Alguna vez has escuchado la frase &quot;mente sana, cuerpo sano&quot;, esta es una frase muy conocida que a menudo escuchamos en personas que practican la actividad fisica, pero tu que piensas &iquest;consideras importante practicar una actividad f&iacute;sica?</span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/259/6.png" style="float:left; height:169px; width:300px" /><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:24px">Veamos el siguiente video:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>

<p><a href="http://https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SSVg9mSiZ8A" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px;">http://https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SSVg9mSiZ8A</a><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:24px">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:24px">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos2/Logo35.PNG" style="float:right; height:155px; width:140px" /></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Actividad fisica e infancia</span></span></p>

<p><strong><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Qu&eacute; actividad f&iacute;sica realizas t&uacute;?</span></span></strong></p>

<p><strong><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Con qu&eacute; frecuencia?&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>

<p><strong><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;C&oacute;mo te sientes despu&eacute;s de alguna actividad f&iacute;sica?&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&iquest;Cu&aacute;l es tu actividad f&iacute;sica favorita?</span></span></strong></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="background-color:#2ecc71">DISE&Ntilde;AR Y CONSTRUIR</span></span></span></span></strong></p>

<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">El d&iacute;a de hoy crear&aacute;s un ensamble el cu&aacute;l consta en un robot entrenador de actividad f&iacute;sica que ayude y cuente las sentadillas que realizas, debe de tener un sensor de movimiento el cual detecte tus brazos cada que bajan al realizar una sentadilla.</span></span></p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos2/Logo36.PNG" style="height:144px; width:699px" /></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:24px"><strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="background-color:#c0392b">&nbsp;CONSTRUCTOR:&nbsp;</span></span></strong>Elaborar&aacute;s un robot entrenador.</span></span>&nbsp;<input name="Boton" type="button" value="Constructor" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:24px"><strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="background-color:#2980b9">&nbsp;COLABORADOR:&nbsp;</span></span></strong>Ayudaras a construir el robot siguiendo la parte 2 del ensamble.</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<input name="Boton2" type="button" value="Colaborador" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="background-color:#f39c12">&nbsp;PROGRAMADOR:&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></span>&nbsp;<span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Se programara alrobot para que realice un conteo de sentadillas, con ayuda del sensor de movimiento.&nbsp;<input name="Boton2" type="button" value="Programador" /></span></span></p>

