<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="background-color:#f1c40f">PREGUNTAR E IMAGINAR</span></span></span></span></strong></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px">El d&iacute;a de hoy explicaras lo que investigaste, as&iacute; como la exposici&oacute;n de tu armado, para ello contar&aacute;s con 20 minutos para reproducir tu armado y probarlo y cada equipo tendr&aacute; 10 minutos para realizar su exposici&oacute;n.</span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="background-color:#2ecc71">DISE</span></span></span><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="background-color:#2ecc71">&Ntilde;AR Y CONSTRUIR&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></strong></p>

