array (
'id' => 142,
'code' => '3.2.2',
'name' => 'Turbina eolica',
'description' => NULL,
'picture' => 'http://therobotcenterapp.com/PortadasCursos/CursoDefault.png',
'editor' => '<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos2/Eduktroic.PNG" /></p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos2/Logo7-2.PNG" style="height:24px; width:688px" /></p>

<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="font-size:26px">&nbsp;<span style="color:#ffffff"><strong><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="background-color:#f1c40f">&nbsp; PREGUNTAR E IMAGINAR&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Como hemos visto en clase anteriores, hay recursos naturales que nos van a servir para satisfacer nuestras necesidades y nos ayudan a sobrevivir. Esos recursos naturales pueden clasificarse en dos:&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">-Recursos Naturales Renovables.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">-Recursos Naturales No Renovables.</span></span></p>

<p><strong><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Los conoces?</span></span></strong></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Si ya conoces el tema, comenta con tus compa&ntilde;eros dos ejemplos de cada uno, si a&uacute;n no lo revisan pide a tu maestro(a) que les mencione un ejemplo.&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos2/Logo9-2.PNG" style="float:left; height:151px; width:230px" /><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">El viento es un recurso natural renovable, si utilizamos la energ&iacute;a que nos ayude a realizar otras actividades. Las turbinas e&oacute;licas son un ejemplo de m&aacute;quinas que aprovechan el viento para generar electricidad.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Vamos a ver el siguiente video para conocer m&aacute;s acerca de c&oacute;mo funcionan:</span></span></p>

<p><img src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/259/image.png" style="float:left; height:169px; width:300px" /><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&nbsp;&quot;Funcionamiento de una turbina e&oacute;lica&quot;</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Siv1n804EM4">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Siv1n804EM4</a></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">duraci&oacute;n: 0:39</span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="background-color:#2ecc71">&nbsp; DISE&Ntilde;AR Y CONSTRUIR&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></strong></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Vamos a dise&ntilde;ar una turbina e&oacute;lica para comprender m&aacute;s acerca de su funcionamiento.</span></span></p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos2/Logo10-2.PNG" style="height:292px; width:281px" /></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos2/Logo11-2.PNG" style="height:109px; width:699px" /></p>

<p>&nbsp;<span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="background-color:#c0392b">&nbsp;CONSTRUCTOR:&nbsp;</span></span>Contruir la parte 1 de la turbina e&oacute;lica.</span></span>&nbsp;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/253/TurbinaEólica PARTE 1.pdf"><input name="BOTON" type="button" value="CONSTRUCTOR" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;<span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#ffffff"><strong><span style="background-color:#2980b9">&nbsp;COLABORADOR:&nbsp;</span></strong></span>Ayudar&aacute;s a tu compa&ntilde;ero a armar la turbina e&oacute;lica.</span></span>&nbsp;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/253/TurbinaEólica PARTE 2.pdf"><input name="BOTON" type="button" value="COLABORADOR" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;<span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#ffffff"><strong><span style="background-color:#f39c12">&nbsp;PROGRAMADOR:&nbsp;</span></strong></span>Sigue la gu&iacute;a de programaci&oacute;n y resuelve los ejercicios.</span></span>&nbsp;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/253/GRUIA PROGRAMACION 3oBLOQUE I Y II 8.pdf"><input name="BOTON" type="button" value="PROGRAMADOR" /></a></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="color:#ffffff"><strong><span style="background-color:#e67e22">&nbsp; ANALIZAR&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">1.-&iquest;Cu&aacute;ntos engranes tiene tu turbina e&oacute;lica?</span></span></strong></p>

<p><strong><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">2.-&iquest;Qu&eacute; funci&oacute;n tiene su engrane motor?</span></span></strong></p>

