'name' => 'ENTENDIENDO LOS ENGRANES',
'description' => NULL,
'picture' => 'http://therobotcenterapp.com/PortadasCursos/271H6105O1UVtDOzEXZTKc1jF0Of6DQnqqH0NbK2.jpeg',
'editor' => '<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Eduktronic.PNG" /></p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo1.PNG" style="height:30px; width:1000px" /></p>

<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="font-size:22px"><span style="background-color:#f1c40f">&nbsp; &nbsp;PREGUNTAR E IMAGINAR&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Qu&eacute; son los engranes?</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Vamos a construir entre todos el concepto de engranes, y vamos a analizar la funci&oacute;n que tienen &eacute;stos.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Observa los engranes y elige la palabra correcta:</span></span></p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo2.PNG" style="height:231px; width:300px" /></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Los engranes son: ruedas/ejes/vigas con dientes/lineas/rayas que</span></span><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"> nos va a permitir transmitir movimiento. Tambi&eacute;n se puede aumentar o disminuir la velocidad y la fuerza con ellos.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo3.PNG" style="float:right; height:331px; width:413px" /></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">El primer engrane que se pone en movimiento se llama: engrane motor / engrane de salida.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">El &uacute;ltimo engrane que se mueve se llama: engrane motor / de salida</span></span>.</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="background-color:#2ecc71">&nbsp; DISE&Ntilde;AR Y CONSTRUIR&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Vamos a poner en pr&aacute;ctica lo que acabamos de leer.&nbsp;Para ver c&oacute;mo funciona</span></span><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">n los engranes vamos a construir un ventilador.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo5.PNG" style="float:right; height:318px; width:219px" /></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:24px"><strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="background-color:#c0392b">CONSTRUCTOR:</span></span></strong> Realiza parte del ventilador. Da click aqui --&gt;</span></span> &nbsp;&nbsp;<input name="Boton" type="button" value="CONSTRUCTOR" />&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="background-color:#2980b9">COLABORADOR:</span></span></strong> Ayuda a construir el ventilador.</span></span><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:24px">Da click aqui --&gt;Da click aqui --&gt;<input name="boton" type="button" value="COLABORADOR " /></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#ffffff"><strong><span style="background-color:#f39c12">PROGRAMADOR:</span></strong></span> Haz girar el ventilador durante 20 segundos hacia el otro lado. recuerda usar el icono de &quot;girar el motor&quot; y despues &quot;activar motor durante&quot;.&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:24px">Da click aqui --&gt;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/253/GUIA PROGRAMACION 2o (2).pdf" target="_blank"><input name="BOTON" type="button" value="PROGRAMADOR" /></a></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo9.PNG" style="float:left; height:188px; width:200px" /></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Cu&aacute;l es el Engrane Motor de tu ensamble?</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Cu&aacute;l es el Engrane de Salida?</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Para qu&eacute; nos sirven los engranes?</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Qu&eacute; engrane gira m&aacute;s r&aacute;pido? &iquest;Por qu&eacute;?</span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo10.PNG" style="float:left; height:162px; width:200px" /></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Deben aplicar la combinaci&oacute;n de engranes necesarias para que su ventilador gire lo m&aacute;s r&aacute;pido posible, sin modificar la potencia del motor. Recuerden los principios revisados al principio de la clase. El Programador debe encargarse de que el ventilador cumpla su funci&oacute;n.</span></span></p>',
'level_id' => NULL,
'created_at' => '2019-08-19 23:00:05',
'updated_at' => '2019-08-26 19:02:13',
),
