'name' => '¿Y SU FORMA PLANA ?',
'description' => NULL,
'picture' => 'http://therobotcenterapp.com/PortadasCursos/thRXAgIfP9zhBhCCpYIOtoy9ZRgH67dJia0VMYAN.jpeg',
'editor' => '<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Eduktronic.PNG" style="height:64px; width:139px" /></p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo1-Clase 4-2.PNG" style="height:30px; width:1000px" /></p>

<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:19.5pt"><span style="background-color:#f1c40f"><span style="color:white">&nbsp; &nbsp;PREGUNTAR E IMAGINAR&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:24px">Si el ma&iacute;z no es plano...<img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo2-Clase4-2.PNG" style="height:130px; width:176px" /></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:24px">&iquest;Entonces por qu&eacute; el cereal est&aacute; plano?</span></span><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo3-Clase4-2.PNG" style="height:108px; width:168px" /></p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo4-Clase4-2.PNG" style="height:195px; width:310px" /><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Como vimos en el v&iacute;deo de la clase anterior, la ma&iacute;z triturado pasa por un Rodillo para poder aplanar los copos de ma&iacute;z. Los Rodillos son cilindros anchos que giran. Con los Rodillos se puede aplanar desde masa para pan, hasta metal y otros materiales.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:19.5pt"><span style="background-color:#2ecc71"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:white">&nbsp; &nbsp;DISE&Ntilde;AR Y CONSTRUIR&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:18.0pt"><span style="background-color:#c0392b"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:white">CONSTRUCTOR:</span></span></span></span></strong></span></span><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Realiza la parte 1 del rodillo.Da click aqu&iacute; --&gt;</span></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/253/RODILLOparte1.pdf"><input name="Boton" type="button" value="CONSTRUCTOR" /></a>&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/256/RODILLO.PNG" style="float:right; height:240px; width:300px" /></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:18.0pt"><span style="background-color:#2980b9"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:white">COLABORADOR:</span></span></span></span></strong> </span></span><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Ayuda con la parte 2, puedes usar peque&ntilde;os pedazos de papel para simular que es ma&iacute;z.Da click aqu&iacute; --&gt;</span></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/253/RODILLOparte2.pdf"><input name="Boton1" type="button" value="COLABORADOR" /></a>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:18.0pt"><span style="background-color:#e67e22"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"><span style="color:white">PROGRAMADOR:</span></span></span></span></strong></span></span><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Deber&aacute;s hacer que el rodillo aplaste los granos de ma&iacute;z.Da click aqu&iacute; --&gt;</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/253/GUIA PROGRAMACION 2o 10.pdf"><input name="Boton2" type="button" value="PROGRAMADOR" /></a></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo9.PNG" style="height:107px; width:114px" /><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Qu&eacute; piezas de tu ensamble simulan el Rodillo que aplana los copos? &iquest;Con qu&eacute; mecanismo funciona tu ensamble?&nbsp;&iquest;Engranes, polea o palancas? &iquest;El Rodillo necesita fuerza para aplastar los copos de ma&iacute;z? &iquest;Qu&eacute; combinaci&oacute;n de engranes ayuda a aumentar la fuerza? Recuerda que cuando se reduce la velocidad, la fuerza aumenta.&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo10.PNG" style="float:left; height:141px; width:174px" />Reto: Colocar&aacute;n el Sensor de Inclinaci&oacute;n.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo27-2.PNG" style="height:82px; width:84px" /></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Reto programaci&oacute;n: Vas a configurar tu programaci&oacute;n para controlar el Rodillo con el sensor de inclinaci&oacute;n. Cuando el sensor de inclinaci&oacute;n est&eacute; &nbsp;hacia arriba, el motor debe comenzar a girar.&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Cuando el Sensor de Inclinaci&oacute;n est&eacute; viendo abajo, el motor debe detenerse. Puedes&nbsp; ponerle al final el icono de Repetir.</span></span><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo28-2.PNG" style="float:right; height:82px; width:82px" /></p>',
'level_id' => NULL,
