<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="background-color:#2980b9">&nbsp;COLABORADOR:&nbsp;</span></span></strong> Apoya al constructor para la realizaci&oacute;n del sistema de riego.</span></span>&nbsp;<input name="Boton1" type="button" value="COLABORADOR" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>

