<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="background-color:#2980b9">&nbsp;COLABORADOR:&nbsp;</span></span>Ayudar&aacute;s al constructor.</span></span>&nbsp;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/253/MANTIS PARTE 2.pdf"><input name="BOTON" type="button" value="COLABORADOR" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#ffffff"><strong><span style="background-color:#f39c12">&nbsp;PROGRAMADOR:&nbsp;</span></strong></span>Mientras tu equipo construye a ti te&nbsp;toca investigar acerca de los insectos, en especifico del que&nbsp;estan armando. Despu&eacute;s realizar&aacute;s la programacion para que tu insecto funcione.</span></span>&nbsp;<input name="BOTON" type="button" value="PROGRAMADOR" /></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="background-color:#e67e22">&nbsp; ANALIZAR&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Qu&eacute; piezas permiten el movimiento de tu robot?</span></span></strong></p>

<p><strong><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Consideras que las piezas simulan el movimiento real de los insectos?</span></span></strong></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos2/Logo12.PNG" style="float:left; height:199px; width:230px" /><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">RETO DE POGRAMACI&Oacute;N</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Agregararas sonidos a tu proramaci&oacute;n que sean grabados por ti que sean similares a los que hace tu insecto.</span></span></p>',
'level_id' => NULL,
'created_at' => '2019-08-22 03:32:37',
'updated_at' => '2019-09-03 20:33:57',
