<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Da click aqui: ----&gt;&nbsp;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/253/GUIA RULETA PARTE 2.pdf"><input name="BOTON" type="button" value="COLABORADOR" /></a></span></span></p>

