<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="background-color:#2980b9">COLABORADOR:</span></span></strong> Ayudaras&nbsp;a dise&ntilde;ar la casa con la&nbsp;puerta ya armada.&nbsp;Da click aqui --&gt;<a href="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/files/253/PUERTA AUTOMATICA parte 2.pdf"><input name="BOTON" type="button" value="COLABORADOR" /></a></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="background-color:#e67e22">PROGRAMADOR:</span></span></strong>&nbsp;Vas a programar la puerta para&nbsp;que se adapte a la estructura de la&nbsp;casa, sin causar que se desarme.&nbsp;Da click aqui --&gt;<input name="BOTON" type="button" value="PROGRAMADOR" /></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="color:#ffffff"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="background-color:#e67e22">&nbsp; ANALIZAR&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></strong></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&nbsp;&iquest;Qu&eacute; mecanismo usa tu puerta autom&aacute;tica?<br />
