<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="color:#ffffff"><strong><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="background-color:#e67e22">&nbsp; ANALIZAR&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><strong><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;C&oacute;mo es que funcion&oacute; tu robot explorador?</span></span></strong></p>

<p><strong><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Qu&eacute; mecanismos lo hacen funcionar?</span></span></strong></p>

<p><strong><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Qu&eacute; funciones puede realizar tu robot exploraor con ayuda de la programaci&oacute;n?</span></span></strong></p>

