<p><img alt="" src="http://therobotcenterapp.com/laravel-filemanager/photos/139/Logos3/Logo9.PNG" style="height:107px; width:114px" />&iquest;Qu&eacute; ventajas tendr&iacute;a el usar buzos robot? ______________________________________________________________________</p>

