<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong><img alt="" src="http://www.therobotcenterapp.com/photos/255/terremotos.jpg" style="height:361px; width:500px" /></strong></span></span></p>

