<p><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong><span style="color:#f39c12">ANALIZAR</span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Qu&eacute; tipo de estructura result&oacute; m&aacute;s resistente (rig&iacute;da)?.</span></span></p>

