<li><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="color:#212529">Da click aqu&iacute;---&gt;<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t5Iw8PeQ6wk"><input name="boton" type="button" value="CONSTRUCTOR PRIN-3" /></a></span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="background-color:#27ae60"><span style="color:white">&nbsp;Colaborador:&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style="color:#212529">El d&iacute;a de hoy te tocar&aacute; armar dos ensambles.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>

