'code' => 'EX.PB.M1-2',
'name' => 'PROGRAMACIÓN',
'description' => 'LOS ALUMNOS CONOCERÁN LOS PASOS PARA REALIZAR LA PROGRAMACIÓN DEL ENSAMBLE.',
'picture' => '/tmp/phpvud0vs',
'editor' => '<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color:#f1c40f"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">PREGUNTAR E IMAGINAR</span></span></strong> </span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Sabes c&oacute;mo funciona un robot?</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Qu&eacute; es una programaci&oacute;n?</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">El Robot es un dispositivo que combina tecnolog&iacute;as mec&aacute;nicas, electr&oacute;nicas el cual controla los motores que son los encargados de generar el movimiento mediante una programaci&oacute;n.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><img alt="" src="http://www.therobotcenterapp.com/photos/256/hub.jpg" style="height:198px; width:300px" /><img alt="" src="http://www.therobotcenterapp.com/photos/256/sensor-de-inclinacion-wedo-20.jpg" style="height:200px; width:200px" /><img alt="" src="http://www.therobotcenterapp.com/photos/256/sensor-de-movimiento-wedo-2.jpg" style="height:132px; width:200px" /><img alt="" src="http://www.therobotcenterapp.com/photos/256/motor.jpg" style="float:left; height:120px; width:200px" /></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">En el software de wedo 2.0 encontraras los siguientes iconos:</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="http://www.therobotcenterapp.com/photos/256/ICONOS.PNG" style="height:557px; width:900px" /></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color:#27ae60"><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>DISE&Ntilde;AR Y CONSTRUIR</strong></span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">1. Construye del software Wedo 2.0 el modelo del sat&eacute;lite.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.therobotcenterapp.com/photos/256/SATELITE.png" style="height:330px; width:500px" /></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">2. Conectar&nbsp; </span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.therobotcenterapp.com/photos/256/conectar-smarthub-lego-education-wedo-2.0.jpg" style="height:178px; width:500px" /></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">3. &nbsp;Este bloque de programaci&oacute;n har&aacute; que el sat&eacute;lite gire con una potencia de motor 1 durante 3 segundos.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt="" src="http://www.therobotcenterapp.com/photos/256/prosatelite.PNG" style="height:155px; width:400px" /></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Para crear el bloque de programaci&oacute;n &nbsp;los equipos deben arrastrar y soltar en la pantalla los bloques que se necesitan para que nuestro ensamble realice el movimiento que el profesor pide.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Presionar el Bloque de inicio (bot&oacute;n amarillo) para ejecutar el programa.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color:#f39c12"><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>ANALIZAR</strong></span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;C&oacute;mo funciona el programa?</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Qu&eacute; hacen los diferentes bloques de programaci&oacute;n?</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="color:#2980b9"><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">INNOVAR</span></span></span></strong></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Los diferentes equipos pueden hacer que el sat&eacute;lite gire durante un per&iacute;odo de tiempo m&aacute;s largo cambiando el n&uacute;mero que se muestra en el bloque de encendido del motor.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>',
'level_id' => NULL,
'created_at' => '2019-11-22 09:14:32',
'updated_at' => '2019-11-22 10:01:09',
),
