<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong><img alt="" src="http://www.therobotcenterapp.com/photos/253/ni%C3%B1o.PNG" style="height:142px; width:300px" />&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><strong>Link del video:&nbsp;<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LiBcur1aqcg">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LiBcur1aqcg</a></strong></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">&iquest;Qu&eacute; objeto se utiliza en el video para poder subir m&aacute;s f&aacute;cilmente los objetos?</span></span></p>

