<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Da click aqu&iacute; ---&gt;<a href="http://www.therobotcenterapp.com/files/255/ROBOT%20BASE%20PARTE%201.pdf"><input name="boton" type="button" value="CONSTRUCTOR" /></a></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>&nbsp;Colaborador:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;El d&iacute;a de hoy te toca construir la parte 2 del ensable de base motr&iacute;z. Agrega sensor de color.</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Da click aqu&iacute; ---&gt;<a href="http://www.therobotcenterapp.com/files/255/ROBOT%20BASE%20PARTE%202.pdf"><input name="boton" type="button" value="COLABORADOR" /></a></span></span></p>

