<p><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:20px">&iquest;Qu&eacute; acciones crees que pueda hacer?</span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="color:#000000"><span style="font-size:20px">&iquest;Qu&eacute; colores usaste?</span></span></span></p>

<hr />
<p><strong><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:26px"><span style="color:#2980b9">INNOVAR</span></span></span></strong></p>

<p><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="color:#000000">Agrega un nuevo color a tu programaci&oacute;n y coloca un sonido o imagen, o cambio de color del brick</span></span></span></p>',
