<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size:18.0pt"><span style="color:#27ae60">Ruleta de Piezas</span></span></span></span></span></p>

