<p><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:20px"><strong><span style="background-color:#2980b9"><span style="color:white">&nbsp;CONSTRUCTOR:</span></span>&nbsp;</strong>La clase de hoy te toca construir la parte 1 de tu ensamble del &quot;puente levadizo&quot;.</span></span></span></span></p>

